{{wikipedia|Ripuarian language}}
===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}

# A [[West Central German]] dialect group, spoken in the northern [[Rhineland]] (including the cities of [[w:Bonn|Bonn]], [[w:Cologne|Cologne]], [[w:Düsseldorf|Düsseldorf]] and [[w:Aachen|Aachen]]), as well as parts of [[w:German-speaking Community of Belgium|German-speaking Belgium]] and south-eastern [[Limburg]] ([[Netherlands]]); linguistically, the least affected by the [[w:High German consonant shift|consonant shift]] of all [[High German]] dialects

